        <num>CC 1858</num>
        <heading>1858.  Lack of capacity of obligee</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1858.  Lack of capacity of obligee
Performance rendered to an obligee without capacity to receive it is valid to the extent of the benefit he derived from it.</p>
        </content>
